cs||fp||va|4|cp|8|AT|^h@2^*BLarry Cohen: ^*N|cp||at|Previously in this series, we covered the "front" of the convention card, culminating with weak two-bids. ACBL members will note that there is one more "front section," namely "other conventional calls." We will deal with those throughout this series, and fill in any gaps at the end. For now, we move to the "back" of the card and start off with DOUBLES.|
