^B@2^*BLarry Cohen: ^*N|cp||at|There is plenty more on this topic (such as follow-ups by opener and responder)'but none of it needs noting on the convention card. I couldn't live without Negative Double. Everyone should play them, and they should be played on all levels (not just the 2- and 3-level). In general, the negative double shows the unbid suits, with the focus on the majors.

